 over people in trials demos, to <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/danny-macaskill-and-hans-rey-conquer-mount-kilimanjaro-by-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">traveling the world on epic adventures with riders like Danny MacAskill</a>, Hans continues to keep us on the edge of our seat.</p><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Kdzyg0GmVJY?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><p>While claiming he’ll never give us his standard mountain bikes, Hans has also been doing a lot more e-bike advocacy recently, which all fits into this clip from Shimano.</p></section></article></main></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d1381dab67899282697fc014bbd924e295814cfe1e78941c1a2b4c3daae5f3c5","category":"Cycling"}